<lyrics>[V1]
 1-(fḍạyl fḍạyl f qlbk fḍạyl tʿlm qlwbnạ ṣḥyḥ ạlạ̹ymạn
 mḥbh wṭạʿh tsạmḥ wdạʿh wṣdq wṭhạrh wṭybh wḥnạn)2
 ạlqrạr- (wmnk yạ yswʿnạ kmạn bntʿlm fy kl ạ̉wạn
 wbạlkẖyr nmly̱ dnytnạ wybqy̱ ạlkwn sʿyd frḥạn)2
 2-(ạ̹lhnạ ạlḥnyn ạ̉bwnạ ạlḥbyb yạ rạfʿ dẖnwbnạ bḥml ạlṣlyb
 hnfḍl tmly nrnm nṣly lạ̉nk yạrby fy ḥbk ʿjyb)2</lyrics>
